            <tbody>
                <row>
                    <entry>Synopsis: <?dbhtml bgcolor="#D4D6EB" ?>
<?dbfo bgcolor="#D4D6EB" ?>
                    </entry>
                    <entry>template("${&lt;macroname&gt;}")</entry>
                </row>
            </tbody>
        </tgroup>
    </informaltable>
    <para><emphasis role="bold">Description:</emphasis> The macro that contains the part of the message that the parser will process. It can also be a macro created by a previous parser of the log path. By default, the parser processes the entire message (<userinput>${MESSAGE}</userinput>).</para>
